{"tid":2133684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台有可能改發三號強風訊號","createTime":"2020-07-31T08:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T11:18:49.000Z","uid":189046,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9bc84d7e691f0a7bcab159d6f55112c7c6af8a","tid":2133684,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"位於南海中北部的季風低壓正逐漸增強，一個熱帶氣旋似乎形成中。<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n現時位於南海中北部的季風低壓中心附近組織鬆散，預計該季風低壓會在未來一兩日逐漸移向海南島至北部灣一帶。當該季風低壓接近海南島一帶時仍有可能進一步發展。若該低壓區發展成為熱帶氣旋，天文台會考慮發出熱帶氣旋警告信號，取代強烈季候風信號。受該低壓區的外圍雨帶影響，華南沿岸未來一兩天會吹強風，有狂風大驟雨及雷暴，海面有湧浪，市民應留意天氣變化。<br />\n<br />\n於 2020 年 7 月 31 日 10 時 00 分 發 出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433d0479fca5c7e861259fdeb9060d321e41e85d","tid":2133684,"uid":343964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef4529d53a8999d8f54ff7d9ec943cb690861c1","tid":2133684,"uid":25952,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"幾好 今日涼左好多"},{"pid":"d73d913573bceaa2a480e3c9804819db410e4bbf","tid":2133684,"uid":22609,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ef4529d53a8999d8f54ff7d9ec943cb690861c1","tid":2133684,"uid":25952,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"幾好 今日涼左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"打緊季候風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c62ad2b29973730750ca1f31c59d90752c53f3","tid":2133684,"uid":98451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"一黎就3號波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730a1839f392c61b9a94a8431e23c0eadb5882bb","